{"lastModified":1768907602268,"uri":"c::32018258056::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Adriatic Sea, Croatia\n\nCheck-in: Saturday from 17:00h  |  Check-out: Saturday until 09:00h\n\n\nOur Catamaran Leopard 45 “Manaphy” is a sleek and stylish sailing vessel that is perfect for exploring the crystal clear waters of Croatia. This luxurious catamaran is designed to provide maximum comfort and space for its guests, making it the ideal choice for a family vacation or a group of friends looking to experience the beauty of the Adriatic Sea.\n\nOne of the most striking features of the Leopard 45 is its spacious and airy design. The catamaran’s wide beam and high ceilings provide a feeling of openness and light, while the large windows and skylights let in plenty of natural light. The main salon and cockpit are connected, creating a seamless indoor-outdoor living space, perfect for enjoying meals and relaxing with friends and family.\n\nThe Leopard 45 has four comfortable double cabins, each with its own private bathroom, and a fifth cabin with bunk beds, providing accommodation for up to 6+1 guests. The cabins are designed to provide a comfortable and relaxing environment, with plenty of storage space and natural light.\n\nLeopard 45 is also equipped with all the latest sailing technology and safety features, making it easy to handle and manoeuvre. The catamaran’s large sail area provides plenty of power for fast and comfortable sailing, while the self-tacking jib makes it easy to handle for sailors of all levels. The catamaran also features a powerful yet quiet generator, air-conditioning, and a water-maker, making it comfortable to live on board.\n\nThe Catamaran Leopard 45 is an excellent choice for exploring the Croatian coastline, with its numerous sheltered bays, hidden beaches, and picturesque islands. The crystal-clear waters of the Adriatic Sea are perfect for swimming, snorkelling, and diving, while the warm climate and mild winds make it perfect for sailing.\n\nThe Leopard 45 is a perfect catamaran for those who value luxury and comfort, and want to explore the Croatian coast in style. With its spacious design, comfortable cabins, and high-quality sailing equipment, the Leopard 45 is the ideal choice for a family vacation or a group of friends looking to experience the beauty of the Adriatic Sea.","blueprint":{"name":"MANAPHY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac95c3e0-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac91f350-1f7b-11f0-a386-c38892cfc239/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac9352e0-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac943d40-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac5ab6b0-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::aca52d30-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac963910-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac968730-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac93c810-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac9304c0-1f7b-11f0-868b-39c6342a7833/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac80b540-1f7b-11f0-b403-f313e3da7ae7/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5495dba0-1f74-11f0-8711-0127e73ef6e2::assets::ac954eb0